{"tid":825220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[平行時空] 女皇陛下港英政府頒佈停工令","createTime":"2018-09-17T12:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T12:26:23.000Z","uid":125508,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"adca0c79ced6e3f40ce93dfc98763990f6210632","tid":825220,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"[女皇陛下港英政府頒佈停工]<br />\n港督會同行政局凌晨決議，明日全港停工停課。<br />\n颳風山竹吹襲香港，香港皇家天文台已於晚上懸掛十號風球，市民務必留在室內，以保安全。<br />\n因應風災嚴重，政府引用條例，頒令明日停工；並已下令民政處、市政局待山竹過後立即清理市面，儘快恢復百業運作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/200820_d91a12e9c25fec80050cf28ab72d4bfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F200820_d91a12e9c25fec80050cf28ab72d4bfe.png&h=a7785992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67ec06e265ae5dfbb74732bfcb9f46ada22aa9e4","tid":825220,"uid":121401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"on9"}]}